Package: eflINLA
Type: Package
Title: Utilities used with INLA by FL
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Frank Lefever
Maintainer: Frank Lefever <flefebvre01@hotmail.com>
Description: Utilities to use with the `INLA` package.
    The functions are mainly used to convert objects so that they have
    a `brms` feel, and, in particular, can be used as `rvars` and `draws_vars`
    with the `posterior` package.
